I&rsquo;m a PhD student in philosophy at Stockholm University, specialized in formal epistemology and semantics. I think and write about rational belief, rational inquiry, and the relation between the two.
I started as a PhD student in February, 2019. Before this, I got a Master&rsquo;s degree in logic from University of Amsterdam in 2018, and a Bachelor&rsquo;s degree in philosophy (with a minor in linguistics) from Stockholm University in 2016.
